    <div class="w-full flex justify-center mb-8 lg:mb-0 lg:w-1/2">
      <img 
        src={profileImg} 
        alt="Foto de perfil" 
        class="w-72 h-72 md:w-[30rem] md:h-[30rem] lg:w-96 lg:h-96 object-cover rounded-full shadow-lg"
      />
    </div>


    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 px-4 md:px-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Hola, soy <span class="text-purple-400 dark:text-purple-300">Jose David</span>, <span class="text-purple-400 dark:text-purple-300">desarrollador de aplicaciones web</span>.
        Tengo una amplia formaci√≥n en mantenimiento de sistemas y <span class="text-purple-400 dark:text-purple-300">testing</span>.
